These generators satisfy the commutation relations of the $\mathfrak{so}(7)$ Lie algebra:

\begin{equation}
[\Sigma^{AB}, \Sigma^{CD}] = g^{AC}\Sigma^{BD} - g^{AD}\Sigma^{BC} - g^{BC}\Sigma^{AD} + g^{BD}\Sigma^{AC}
