Using the relation $[\gamma^i, \gamma^j] = 2i\epsilon_{ijk}\gamma^5\gamma^k$ (where $\gamma^5 = i\gamma^0\gamma^1\gamma^2\gamma^3$), we find:

\begin{equation}
