\end{equation}

Let us verify that this 4D Dirac equation satisfies the required properties. First, we check that the 4D gamma matrices $\gamma^\mu$ satisfy the Clifford algebra relation:

\begin{equation}
\{\gamma^\mu, \gamma^\nu\} = 2g^{\mu\nu}I_4
