In the standard representation, the 4D gamma matrices are:

\begin{align}
\gamma^0 &= \begin{pmatrix} I_2 & 0 \\ 0 & -I_2 \end{pmatrix} \\
\gamma^i &= \begin{pmatrix} 0 & \sigma_i \\ -\sigma_i & 0 \end{pmatrix}
