\{\gamma^0, \gamma^0\} &= 2(\gamma^0)^2 = 2\begin{pmatrix} I_2 & 0 \\ 0 & -I_2 \end{pmatrix}^2 = 2\begin{pmatrix} I_2 & 0 \\ 0 & I_2 \end{pmatrix} = 2I_4 \\
